------------------------
Surf_buck-fever
Created by Buck Nasty
------------------------

This is circular type combat map.

- Bounce off the bullseye bounce pads to launch yourself across the map.
- The bounce pads have 2 pushes on them:
  1. Center - more powerful
  2. Outer - less powerful
- There is a 4 way directional chevron arrow above each pad to launch you in that specific direction.
- There are also chevrons on the walkable water areas that push you towards the bounce pads to launch you back on to the surf.
- If you fall you are spawned in the middle of the map and you have to walk to the bounce pads (the chevron paths are accessible to go faster).
- Each team is color coded:
  Terrorists : RED
  Counter-Terrorists : BLUE

Skybox - people tell me hipshot.

I'd rather not ask for constructive criticism cause I honestly don't care, this map is the way I like it. Although, compliments are welcome.

-- Buck Nasty
